body.p:
To make your documents fully accessible (PDF/UA1), do the following:

In your customization CSS, specify
          fonts for all elements and for all page margin boxes. There should be no text that falls
          back to the basic provided fonts (Times, Courier, etc.). For instance, you can
          use::root { font-family: Arial }
@page {
    @top-left {font-family: Arial }
    ...
}

Specify an alt attribute with a description on any image, or better,
          use the alt DITA element.

Change the Chemistry invocation from the build.xml file, adding the
          argument -pdf-ua. There are two targets to change:
            chemistry and chemistry.embedded.
